divs: Sighting DetailsI mistakenly posted the low res pics from this morning's report. these images are the Hi-Res images of the anamoly. Has anyone seen this 'design' in a UFO before? I have about 15 pics in all. This first pic is zoomed in and I use Photoshop CS to auto-adjust Contrast and Levels on all images, though I have the originals; you can zoom in pretty good to this images. The second pic is Auto Contrast. The third pis is Auto contrast and shows object as it passes by the phone wires at my back patio; it must be some 1000-1500 yds behind and above the wire, heading N.
